ntly received or are receiving treatment with a pure opioid agonist.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/51187/', '', 'Acamprosate, Disulfiram, Nalmefene, Nicotine, Buprenorphine, Buprenorphine', 'Acamprosate, Varenicline, Disulfiram, Methadone, Nalmefene, Nicotine, Methadone', 1767369485);
